<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Categories : Invitation</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/invitation.css">

  <!-- favicon -->
  <link href="Resources/favicon.ico" rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" />

  <style media="screen">
    #testimonials {
      background-image: url("Resources/Image_Rejection.jpg");
      color: #fff;
      height: 450px;
      width: 100%;
      position: absolute;
      top: 1680px;
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/39acc06808.js"></script>

  <!-- bootstrap-->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Montserrat:wght@100;700;800;900&family=Ubuntu:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
  <section id="upperSection">
    <div class="categoryUpperSection">
      <img class="background-img" src="Resources/Image_Five.png" alt="img-not-found">
      <i class="fa fa-comments stc" aria-hidden="true">student connect</i>
      <h1 class="CategoryHeading"> Invitation </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="categoryIntro">
      <h1 class="categoryIntro-txt">Invite people from your event or find events to attend</h1>
      <!-- <h3 class="FriendshipQoute">“A good friend is like a four-leaf clover: hard to find and lucky to have.”- Irish Proverb</h3> -->
    </div>

    <div class="categorySlide">
      <h1 class="categoryTips">Tips on how to find events to attend or invite people to events online</h1>
      <div id="categorySlideTips" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <p>1.Be excited, show entusiasm,and care about them</p>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <p>2.Provide as much details about the event as you can.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <p>3.Make the person you're inviting feel welcome.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="connections">
    <form action="/invitation" method="post">
      <div class="connectSection">
        <h1 class="startConnection">Start your connection</h1>

        <div class="connectionButtons">
          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg connect" type="submit" name="invitationConnectbtn" value="Coninvitation">Connect</button>
          <button class="btn btn-dark btn-lg disconnect" type="submit" name="invitationDisConnectbtn" value="Disinvitation">Disconnect</button>
          <button class="btn btn-danger btn-lg report" type="submit" name="reportbtn" value="reportinvitation">Report</button>
        </div>


        <div class="User1">
          <video id="video" height="492" autoplay> </video>
        </div>

        <div class="User2">
          <video id="videoTwo" height="492" autoplay> </video>
        </div>

      </div>

    </form>

  </section>

  <section id="rejection">
    <div class="rejectionSection">
      <h1 class="rejection-txt">Incase things dont go according to plan, we still got you covered!</h1>
      <h3 class="tipsTestimonial">After dealing with multiple rejections, I implemented the tips I got from this platform to increase the the number of people attending my events. ~ Footho Serina </h3>
      <div class="rejectionSmalltxt">
        <p>“Character cannot be developed in ease and quiet. Only through experiences of trial and suffering can the soul be strengthened, vision cleared, ambition inspired and success achieved.”</p>
      </div>
      <!-- <img class="imgRejection" src="Resources/failed_love.jpg" alt="img-not-found"> -->
    </div>

    <div id="testimonials" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <h1 class="rejection-heading">Tips on how to deal with people rejecting your events</h1>
      <div class="container carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <h1 class="carousel-txt">1.Understand that not everyone can trust people online.</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <h1 class="carousel-txt-two">2.Reflect on your approach and learn from mistakes.</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="carousel-item">
          <h1 class="carousel-txt-three">3.Rejection is part of the journey, embrace it.</h1>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonials" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#testimonials" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="relationship.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
</body>

</html>
